data.description: HUGE LOT!! AMAZING move in ready home located in highly desirable Northern Terrace of Providence. Community features 3 pools, clubhouse, gym, BBQ area, playground, entertainment room and more. This home is 2,032sqft, 4 bed (1 down), 3 full bath(1 down), 2 car garage. House is located 1 block from community amenities. Open layout, security screen door, upgraded laminate floors, fireplace, surround sound, blinds, granite counters w/ island, electric stove(gas hookup too), stainless steel appliances, washer, dryer, fridge included, tons of natural light, my Q garage door opener and upgraded bathroom fixtures. Wood plank stairs, large loft w/ storage cabinets and surround sound pre-wire, large primary bed and ensuite w/ raised vanity and dual sinks, LARGE walk in closet, sep tub/shower. Secondary bath has raised vanity w/ dual sinks and tub/shower combo. One of the largest lots in the community w/ covered patio, artifical turf and HUGE SIDE YARD! POOL SIZE LOT!!
